    <div class="container-fluid">
	<div class="row text-center mb-3">
		<h1>Accueil de ProStage</h1>
		<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Suspendisse congue erat quam, eget sagittis leo porta et. Maecenas egestas posuere dolor, sed tincidunt nunc semper vel. Vivamus in nibh nisl. Curabitur dignissim metus mauris, non porttitor leo semper quis. Nunc molestie nisl at hendrerit dapibus. Vestibulum non sodales massa. Phasellus efficitur, metus at sodales malesuada, arcu dolor euismod arcu, sed rutrum tellus leo id nunc. Donec tristique risus porta odio tempus, eget tempus nulla euismod. Praesent sodales velit arcu, et pharetra sem congue sed. Vivamus auctor gravida purus. Suspendisse pellentesque massa id lorem condimentum auctor. Cras facilisis pharetra est vitae eleifend. Morbi posuere id libero at ullamcorper. Pellentesque congue dolor iaculis eros mattis, quis sodales turpis sollicitudin.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="row">
				<div class="col-md-4 text-center mb-3">
						<a href="{{path('prostages_stagesListe')}}" target="_blank" class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-lg center">Voir les Stages</a>
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-4 text-center">
						<a href="{{path('prostages_entreprises')}}" target="_blank" class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-lg center">Voir les Entreprises</a>
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-4 text-center">
						<a href="{{path('prostages_formations')}}" target="_blank" class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-lg center">Voir les Formations</a>
				</div>
	</div>

	<div class="row">
		<div class="card text-black bg-light mb-3"><h5 class="card-header">
			Derniers Stages ajoutes
		</h5></div>
	</div>
	
	<div class="row">
		{% for ressourceCourante in ressourcesStage %}
		<div class="col-md-3">
            <div class="card text-black bg-light mb-3">
                <h5 class="card-header">
					{{ressourceCourante.titre}}
				</h5>
				<div class="card-body">
					<p class="card-text">
						{{ressourceCourante.mission}}
					</p>
					<p class="btn-group">
						<a href="{{path('prostages_stages',{id:ressourceCourante.id})}}" target="_blank" class="btn btn-outline-dark">Visiter</a>
						<a href="mailto:{{ressourceCourante.email}}" target="_blank" class="btn btn-outline-dark">Email</a>
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		{% endfor %}

		<div class="row">
			<div class="card text-black bg-light mb-3"><h5 class="card-header">
				Dernieres Entreprises ajoutees
			</h5></div>
		</div>

		<div class="row">
		{% for ressourceCourante in ressourcesEntreprise %}
		<div class="col-md-3">
            <div class="card text-black bg-light mb-3">
					<h5 class="card-header">
					{{ressourceCourante.nom}}
					</h5>
					<div class="card-body">
					<p class="card-text">
						<strong>Adresse : </strong>{{ressourceCourante.adresse}}
					</p>
					<p class="card-text">
						<strong>Activite : </strong>{{ressourceCourante.activite}}
					</p>
					<p class="card-text">
						<strong>Siteweb : </strong>{{ressourceCourante.siteweb}}
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		{% endfor %}

	</div>

{% endblock %}
